<HEAD>Striking Writers Return to Picket Lines</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto LA3</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOHN HORN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
